OL,3,CToy car bursts into flames killing
OL,4,Ccats and destroying home
OL,6,FHamshire and Isle of Wight Fire &
OL,7,FRescue Service told Lucy Warhurst they
OL,8,Fhave dealt with 36 lithium-ion battery
OL,9,Ffires so far this year compared to
OL,10,Fjust one in 2019.
OL,12,FA mother from Hampshire is warning
OL,13,Fpeople about the dangers of lithium-
OL,14,Fion batteries following a devastating
OL,15,Fflat fire.
OL,17,FMolly's two-year-old daughter had an
OL,18,Felectric toy car which was on charge
OL,19,Fwhen it suddenly burst into flames.
