OL,6,FMolly said the flames were "crawling
OL,7,Fup the wall" in the lounge and the
OL,8,Fpair were forced to flee their home.
OL,10,FThey were able to escape but their two
OL,11,Fcats were killed and their home was
OL,12,Fdestroyed.
OL,14,FSix months on and they're yet to move
OL,15,Fback in.
