OL,6,FMolly says she doesn't want anyone
OL,7,Felse to suffer, adding: "It's just
OL,8,Fspreading awareness of how to be
OL,9,Fcareful and just knowing the dangers
OL,10,Fbecause I wouldn't have thought this
OL,11,Fwould have happened at all."
OL,13,FHampshire and Isle of Wight Fire and
OL,14,FRescue Service says there has been a
OL,15,Fhuge surge in battery-related fires.
OL,17,FIn 2019 there was one recorded fire
OL,18,Fwithin Hampshire and the Isle of Wight
OL,19,Fbut this year there has been 36 so far.
