OL,6,FJohn Amos, Operations Area Manager,
OL,7,Fsaid: "We need to buy from a reputable
OL,8,Fplace, we need to ensure it's got the
OL,9,Fsafety mark on it, and actually that
OL,10,Fwe are taking responsibility for it,
OL,11,Fso we are reading the instructions,
OL,12,Fwe're using the correct charger for
OL,13,Fthe device, and we're looking for any
OL,14,Fproblems that it may have, any
OL,15,Foverheating, any brown marks and
OL,16,Fanything like that that may affect it."
